name: Retro Heart by AirOhMail: balloon and card in one
description:
Go retro!  This heart shaped balloon and greeting card is a special way to show someone you care.

Before giving this unique AirOhMail balloon-card, you can personalize card with your own message. This birthday balloon needs no helium, so it's safe to send through the post or give as a gift for all ages. The balloon is inflated from the card to a diameter of 14 inches, and the card acts as a stand for the balloon. 

Give a card that stands out from the rest. Blow up your greeting card and send along a smile today!

Please choose one option:
1. Send it to me so I can personalize exactly the way I want.
2. Send it to my recipient and include a note for me.*

*If you would like us to send it directly to your recipient, we will follow up your purchase with an email asking for the message you want printed, the date you would like AirOhMail delivered, and to make sure we have the correct delivery address.
